{"tid":1148513,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"想搵啲類似Diablo 2 嘅遊戲玩","createTime":"2019-05-10T13:44:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-13T13:41:33.000Z","uid":48498,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"02562040d29f141cbebbb41b1b48df345a7728d1","tid":1148513,"uid":48498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T13:44:16.000Z","msg":"好掛住打D2打寶，唔同職業平衝同有故事嘅日子。對上一隻真係滿足到部分嘅已經係Dark Soul 3 ，但係冇技能系統始終無咩個人風格，無得好似嗰陣淨係一隻死靈又可以玩召喚，又可以玩骨玩毒嘅趣味性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n求推薦，D2已經玩到儘咁濟，每隻職，每款玩法都玩過。畫面已經開始接受唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：D3嘅耐玩程度，地圖同系統連皮都比唔上D2"},{"pid":"6841545ed137a06dc43428b7cfc7a5d4dc7c159f","tid":1148513,"uid":79793,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T13:45:45.000Z","msg":"Poe"},{"pid":"d9300cd562c6e97385c02a40c15c0a31d064f0a1","tid":1148513,"uid":18844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6841545ed137a06dc43428b7cfc7a5d4dc7c159f","tid":1148513,"uid":79793,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T13:45:45.000Z","msg":"Poe"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T13:46:29.000Z","msg":"POE!"},{"pid":"0600a9a705e0233dac08e2d75ac028d7e5d5820d","tid":1148513,"uid":48498,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T13:50:08.000Z","msg":"官網有啲亂，依家研究下先，洗唔洗課金嗰啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"9cb2578e37388e0db0a4430811351e282730cfbb","tid":1148513,"uid":113373,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T13:51:10.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">反對修訂逃犯條例 香港的終局之戰</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">立法會集會:<br />\n5月11日 星期六 早上8:30 (開會討論修訂逃犯條例)<br />\n<br />\n若不能阻止立法，稍後立法會二讀/三讀時，行動將升級<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事態危急<br />\n一定要阻止立法<br />\n否則香港直送中國受審<br />\n到時中國話你犯咗中國法律 無需證據 無需理由<br />\n就可以光明正大係香港夾你返中國 <br />\n坐黑獄 洗你腦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">此修例禍害大於23條立法<br />\n23條&gt;&gt;&gt;(需危害國家安全，香港審判，香港監禁)<br />\n<br />\n修訂逃犯條例 &gt;&gt;&gt;(莫需有，中國政府可任意控告香港人多達46條罪行，香港會配合執法將你拘捕，移交中國審判及監禁，無需證據 無需理由)</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"b1ce14a6f839aeea0bc5a4a9c0609b5052bac73f","tid":1148513,"uid":18844,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T13:54:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/27jXgFD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F27jXgFD.png&h=2bedc633&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\nsynthesis就來完季~ 一早棄左game~<br />\n頭先入去點一點6L,90粒fuse KO, 你老味完季前先俾我點到...<br />\n<br />\n有需要錢可以pm我~<br />\n<br />\nin game id: KemicalReaction"},{"pid":"4fd13d221984ef669bb494bde815a482b2f65799","tid":1148513,"uid":18844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0600a9a705e0233dac08e2d75ac028d7e5d5820d","tid":1148513,"uid":48498,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T13:50:08.000Z","msg":"官網有啲亂，依家研究下先，洗唔洗課金嗰啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T13:55:10.000Z","msg":"課金主要係買倉庫頁, currency頁, 地圖頁, 高級頁(賣野)"},{"pid":"f1aee8d257a651e115f1f2e6499812dd32cd8bf5","tid":1148513,"uid":51225,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T13:56:18.000Z","msg":"Torchlight, Grim Dawn.... 但坦白從來冇一隻好玩過Diablo 2"},{"pid":"9856505ffda6741141e2c1885993c7ec4bd48511","tid":1148513,"uid":51225,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T13:57:18.000Z","msg":"唔記得講仲有Titan Quest，都ok好玩，而且steam成日減價"},{"pid":"c2cc3bfce86dfde665fa0381cd555e8d8cb6d7e4","tid":1148513,"uid":18844,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f1aee8d257a651e115f1f2e6499812dd32cd8bf5","tid":1148513,"uid":51225,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T13:56:18.000Z","msg":"Torchlight, Grim Dawn.... 但坦白從來冇一隻好玩過Diablo 2"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T14:00:03.000Z","msg":"POE 世界第一, 不服來辯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\